description:
&lt;p&gt;This is a fixed term post for 12 months. If you are a SBUHB employee you will need to secure permission from your line manager before applying for this post.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We have an exciting opportunity for an innovative and competent Speech and Language Therapist to join our school aged paediatric Speech and Language Therapy team working in the Swansea Bay area on a fixed-term contract for 12 months.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As part of our school age team, the successful candidate will work alongside other Speech and Language therapists to assess and treat children and young people with a range of speech, language and communication needs who are educated in Specialist Teaching Facilities across Swansea. An interest and understanding of ASD and learning disabilities is essential.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post will suit a Speech and Language Therapist who is looking to promote multi-disciplinary and multi-agency working. It provides an opportunity to develop skills in the training and education of school staff, partnership working with parents and the development of therapy programmes.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In our SLT department, we offer supported CPD through:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;1:1 line management meetings&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Clinical supervision in peer groups&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Specific support from Lead SLTs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coaching, work based learning and external courses&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Opportunities for service improvement through audit and evidence based practice&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Regular meetings as a paediatric team as well as whole service development days&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Admin staff experienced in information management systems.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The ability to speak Welsh is desirable for this post; Welsh and/or English speakers are equally welcome to apply.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Ann MilliganClinical Lead SLT - School Age Services&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Telephone number 01792 517863&lt;/p&gt;
